<plot>The two stars of Leos Janácek's "The Cunning Little Vixen", Eva Jenis and Thomas Allen discuss their roles, the music and perform an aria from the opera. Stage Director, Nicholas Hytner and Designer, Bob Crowley capture beautifully the central themes of the eternal cycle of Nature. The Orchestre de Paris is conducted by Sir Charles Mackerras an expert interpreter of Janácek's works.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?222216</url></doc>
